descriptionHtml:
This is something I spent hours trying to work out. I have finally created my first custom clothing.

It is modeled off the execution hood!

You can find it in game in the bannered mare upstairs lying on the ground.
alternatively you could spawn it in.

 WARNING: If picking up the mask from the bannered you will get bounty if you are seen as I have yet to find out how to make the item non-stealable. :D

Thanks
author: Jitch
